modName: UNP Clothing Resource Retextures - Crop Top and Jeans
summary: Texture Replacer for Crop Top and Jeans from Dimonized UNP Clothing Resources
descriptionHtml:
This mod replaces the textures of the Crop Top and Jeans from Dimonized UNP Clothing Resources. I used texture resources off Google and added the texture to the original via Photoshop. I hope ya'll like the mod.

I was going for a modern female fashion look with this mod. 

You NEED the original mod for this to work,after you install the original mod overwrite the textures with these.

This mod is NMM supported.

Link to original mod (required):https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/11882/?

The texture resolutions are 2k.
